            function showRatings(supplier, ratingContainer){
                $('.supplierInfoPopup', $(ratingContainer)).clone(true).lightbox_me({
                    centered: true, 
                    overlayCSS: {background: '#fff', opacity: 0.8},
                    destroyOnClose: true
                });
                GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'PROD-270', 'showRatings', supplier, 1, true);
            }

	<script type="text/javascript" nonce="q9qsq10594e1qf6gbpc6lfj6ss">
	        function GAQPushTransition(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction) {
	        	serialiseEvent(new GAQEvent(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction));
	        }
	
	        function GAQPushSecureTransition(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction,domain) {
	        	serialiseSecureEvent(new GAQEvent(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction),domain);
	        }
	
	        function GAQPush(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction) {
	        	pushEvent(new GAQEvent(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction));
	        }
	
	        function GAQPushPage(gaq_event_name, action){
	        	pushPageEvent(new GAQPageEvent(gaq_event_name, action));
	        }
	        
	        function GAQPushLinkByPost(form) {
	        	pushLinkByPostEvent(new GAQLinkByPostEvent(form));
	        }
	
	        $(document).ready(function() {
	        	try {
	        		if ('/LoadingSearchResults.do' !== window.location.pathname) {
		        		$(deserialiseEvents(true)).each(function() {
		        			pushEvent(this);
		        		});
	        		}
	        	} catch (err) {
	        		
	        	}
	        });
	
	        var cookie_name = 'gaw_track';
	        
	        var accountPrefixes = new Array();
	        accountPrefixes.push('m');
	
	        function serialiseEvent(gaq_event) {
	        	var eventList = deserialiseEvents(false);
	        	if (!isDuplicateGAEvent(eventList, gaq_event)) {
	        		eventList.push(gaq_event);
	        	}
	        	$.cookies.set(cookie_name, $.toJSON(eventList));
	        }
	
	        function serialiseSecureEvent(gaq_event,domain) {
	        	$.cookies.set(cookie_name, $.toJSON(gaq_event),{domain:domain});
	        }
	
	        function deserialiseEvents(deleteAfterRead) {
	        	var events = new Array();
	
	        	if ($.cookies.get(cookie_name) !== null) {
	        		var json = $.evalJSON($.toJSON($.cookies.get(cookie_name)));
	
	        		if (json instanceof Array) {
	        			$(json).each(function() {
	        				events.push(new GAQEvent(this.gaq_event_name, this.category, this.action, this.label, this.value, this.non_interaction));
	        			});
	        		}
	        		else {
	        			events.push(new GAQEvent(json.gaq_event_name, json.category, json.action, json.label, json.value, json.non_interaction));
	        		}
	        	}
	        	
	        	if (deleteAfterRead) {
	        		$.cookies.set(cookie_name, null);
	        	}
	        	
	        	return events;
	        }
	
	        function pushEvent(e) {
	        	try{
	        		_gaq.push([e.gaq_event_name, e.category, e.action, e.label, e.value, e.non_interaction]);
	        		for (var i = 0; i < accountPrefixes.length; i++) {
	        			var prefix = accountPrefixes[i];
	        			_gaq.push([prefix + '.' + e.gaq_event_name, e.category, e.action, e.label, e.value, e.non_interaction]);	
	        		}
	        	}catch(err){
	        	
	        	}
	        }
	
	        function pushPageEvent(e) {
	        	try{
	        		_gaq.push([e.gaq_event_name, e.action]);
	        		for (var i = 0; i < accountPrefixes.length; i++) {
	        			var prefix = accountPrefixes[i];
	        			_gaq.push([prefix + '.' + e.gaq_event_name, e.action]);
	        		}
	        	}catch(err){
	        	
	        	}
	        }
	        
	        function pushLinkByPostEvent(e) {
	        	_gaq.push([e.gaq_event_name, e.form]);
	        	for (var i = 0; i < accountPrefixes.length; i++) {
	        		var prefix = accountPrefixes[i];
	        		_gaq.push([prefix + '.' + e.gaq_event_name, e.form]);
	        	}
	        }
	
	        
	        /*
	         * Transition management
	         * Make sure duplicate events are not tracker on page transition
	         */
	        function isDuplicateGAEvent(existingEvents, newEvent) {
	        	var key = newEvent.category + '#' + newEvent.action + '#' + newEvent.label;
	        	var found = false;
	        	for (var i = 0; i < existingEvents.length; i++) {
	        		var existingEventsKey = existingEvents[i].category + '#' + existingEvents[i].action + '#' + existingEvents[i].label;
	        		if (existingEventsKey === key) {
	        			found = true;
	        			break;
	        		}
	        	}
	        	return found;
	        }
	        
	
	        /**
	         * Object representation of the Google Analytics _gaq.push(...) method
	         * https://developers.google.com/analytics/devguides/collection/gajs/eventTrackerGuide
	         */
	        function GAQEvent(gaq_event_name, category, action, label, value, non_interaction) {
	        	this.gaq_event_name = gaq_event_name;
	        	this.category = category;
	        	this.action = action;
	        	this.label = label;
	        	this.value = value;
	        	this.non_interaction = non_interaction;
	        }
	
	        function GAQPageEvent(gaq_event_name, action) {
	        	this.gaq_event_name = gaq_event_name;
	        	this.action = action;
	        }
	        
	        function GAQLinkByPostEvent(form) {
	        	this.gaq_event_name = '_linkByPost';
	        	this.form = form;
	        }
        </script>

				}

        <script type="text/javascript" src="/js/jquery.jgrowl.js"></script>
			<script type="text/javascript" nonce="q9qsq10594e1qf6gbpc6lfj6ss">

				var Rbks = {
						index: -1, ckName:'Rbks___', sep:'|', totalShown: 0,
						wait: function() {
							 return Math.max( 3000,
									 Math.ceil((Math.random()*(97000/4))+1) );
						}
					};
		
				Rbks.json = 
					[
								{'id':'9dc68dba0f406003453979e6ab5b902b',
								
	
								'msg':'New Booking! A customer from <img class=\"flagImg\" src=\"http://cdn.rcstatic.com/images/flags-sml/gb.png\"> has booked a car in Vilnius'},
								{'id':'bb3d821c7faeb9ef3690558ccf3f4cf9',
								
	
								'msg':'New Booking! A customer from <img class=\"flagImg\" src=\"http://cdn.rcstatic.com/images/flags-sml/de.png\"> has booked a car in Vilnius'},
								{'id':'e387c41d1c41270bfba1557ce1b8018f',
								
	
								'msg':'New Booking! A customer from <img class=\"flagImg\" src=\"http://cdn.rcstatic.com/images/flags-sml/gb.png\"> has booked a car in Vilnius'},
								{'id':'6e01b2b81874a50010194ba3fb688feb',
								
	
								'msg':'New Booking! A customer from <img class=\"flagImg\" src=\"http://cdn.rcstatic.com/images/flags-sml/dk.png\"> has booked a car in Vilnius'}];
			
				Rbks.getIndex = function() {
					if(++Rbks.index >= Rbks.json.length) {
						Rbks.index = Rbks.json.length;
						return -1;
					}
					return Rbks.index + 0;
				};				

				Rbks.run = function(index) {
					if(Rbks.json.length < 1 || index < 0 || index >= Rbks.json.length) return false;
					
					var interval = Rbks.wait();
					setTimeout(function() {
						$.jGrowl(Rbks.json[index].msg,
		 					{sticky: false, position: "top-right", life: 4800,
				    			beforeClose: function(e,m) {
				    				new Rbks.run(Rbks.getIndex());
				    		    }
		 					}
						);
			         }, interval);
				};
			
			    var bookingAlertRbksDocReady = function() {
			        	new Rbks.run(Rbks.getIndex()); 
			    };
			    
			    
		        		$(document).ready(bookingAlertRbksDocReady);
		        	</script>

		function loginTrack() {

			$(document).ready(function() {
				$('.badge-unread').show();

				var nameEQ = "tj_loyaltyComp_notif=true";
				var ca = document.cookie.split(';');
				for(var i = 0; i < ca.length; i++) {
					var c = ca[i];
					while(c.charAt(0) == ' ') {
						c = c.substring(1,c.length);
					}
					if(c.indexOf(nameEQ) == 0) {
						$("#headerNotifLoyaltyComp").hide();
						$('.badge-unread').hide();
					}
				}
				$('.inline-message.hide-on a.hide').click(function () {
					$(this).parent().slideUp();
					document.cookie = 'tj_loyaltyComp_notif=true;path=/;';
					$('.badge-unread').hide();
				});
			});
		
			$(function(){
				$("input[name=remember-me]").click(function(){
					if($(this).is(":checked")){
						this.value=true;
					}else{
						this.value = false;
					}
				});
			});

<script type="text/javascript" nonce="q9qsq10594e1qf6gbpc6lfj6ss">
	var sessionIdJsVariable = '49CA5C96F09A7D6B27821F912D463145.node379a';
	/* Added 'Crm' postfix so these variables don't interefere with existing JS */
	var serverNameCrm = 'www.rentalcars.com';
	var secureServerCrm = 'secure.rentalcars.com';

	$(document).ready( function (event) {
		$('.rch-toggle').click(function () {
			// Toggle buttons when burger menu clicked
			if ($('.rch-navigation').css('display') == 'none'){
				$('.rch-navigation').css('display', 'table-cell');
				$('.rch-welcome-message').hide();
			}else{
				$('.rch-navigation').hide();
				$('.rch-navigation-button').removeClass("active");
			}
		});

		// Clicking away closes dropdowns
		$('html').click(function() {
			$('.rch-drop-down').hide();
			$('.rch-navigation-button').removeClass("active");
		});

		// Tapping away closes dropdowns
		$('html').bind('touchend', function() {
			$('.rch-drop-down').hide();
			$('.rch-navigation-button').removeClass("active");
		});

		// Close all dropdowns and open specific one on click
		$('.rch-navigation-button').click(function(event){

			if ($(this).hasClass("active")) {
				// Set all tab buttons and dropdowns to default
				$('.rch-drop-down').hide();
				$('.rch-navigation-button').removeClass("active");
			} else {
				// Set all tab buttons and dropdowns to default
				$('.rch-drop-down').hide();
				$('.rch-navigation-button').removeClass("active");

				// Apply clicked style and show dropdown
				$(this).children(".rch-drop-down").show();
				$(this).addClass("active");
			}

			// Apply clicked style and show dropdown (GlobalNav)
			if ($('#rch-select-global-nav').hasClass("active")) {
				$("#rch-global-navigation").show();
			}

            // Apply clicked style and show dropdown (LangSelectRedesign)
            if ($('#rch-select-language').hasClass("active")) {
                $("#rch-language-select").show();
            }
			event.stopPropagation();
		});


		$('.rch-drop-down').click(function(event){
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$('.rch-drop-down, .rch-navigation-button').bind('touchend', function(event) {
			event.stopPropagation();
	});
	});

	<!-- Find my booking panel -->
	var forgotBookingServerName = "www.rentalcars.com";

	

		$(document).ready(function () {
			var loggedInComp = "false";
			$('.promo_sign_in_btn').click(function(e) {
				var $modalPromoCustoms = $(".modal_promo input[name='signupSigninModalCustomName']");
				var $modalPromoCustom;
				$modalPromoCustoms.each(function(index) {
					if($(this).val() === "LoyaltyRefundCompetition") {
						$modalPromoCustom = $(this);
					}
				});
				if($modalPromoCustom != null) {
					GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'FE-3419, logged-in: ' + loggedInComp, 'Home page - Opened Modal - lt', "", 1, true);
					$modalPromoCustom.parent(".modal_promo").lightbox_me({
						centered: true,
						overlayCSS: {
							background: "#000",
							opacity: 0.8
						}
					});
				} else {
					var data = {};
					data['layout'] = 'loyaltyRefundCompetition';
					$.ajax({
						type: "POST",
						url: '/RequestData.do;jsessionid=49CA5C96F09A7D6B27821F912D463145.node379a',
						data: data,
						cache: false,
						success: function(data) {
							$("#loyaltyRefundCompetitionLoad").html(data);
							GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'FE-3419, logged-in: ' + loggedInComp, 'Home page - Opened Modal - lt', "", 1, true);
							var $modalPromoCustoms = $(".modal_promo input[name='signupSigninModalCustomName']");
							var $modalPromoCustom;
							$modalPromoCustoms.each(function(index) {
								if($(this).val() === "LoyaltyRefundCompetition") {
									$modalPromoCustom = $(this);
								}
							});
							$modalPromoCustom.parent(".modal_promo").lightbox_me({
								centered: true,
								overlayCSS: {
									background: "#000",
									opacity: 0.8
								}
							});
						},
						error: function() {
						}
					});
				}
			});
		});
	

		function createAccountModalOpen() {
			$('#btn-sign-in').removeClass('active');
			var $modalPromoCustoms = $(".modal_promo input[name='signupSigninModalCustomName']");
			var $modalPromoCustom;
			$modalPromoCustoms.each(function(index) {
				if($(this).val() === "CreateAccount") {
					$modalPromoCustom = $(this);
				}
			});
			if($modalPromoCustom != null) {
				$modalPromoCustom.parent(".modal_promo").lightbox_me({
					centered: true,
					overlayCSS: {
						background: "#000",
						opacity: 0.8
					}
				});
			} else {
				var data = {};
				data['layout'] = 'createAccountModal';
				$.ajax({
					type: "POST",
					url: '/RequestData.do;jsessionid=49CA5C96F09A7D6B27821F912D463145.node379a',
					data: data,
					cache: false,
					success: function(data) {
						$("#modal_create_account").html(data);
						var $modalPromoCustoms = $(".modal_promo input[name='signupSigninModalCustomName']");
						var $modalPromoCustom;
						$modalPromoCustoms.each(function(index) {
							if($(this).val() === "CreateAccount") {
								$modalPromoCustom = $(this);
							}
						});
						$modalPromoCustom.parent(".modal_promo").lightbox_me({
							centered: true,
							overlayCSS: {
								background: "#000",
								opacity: 0.8
							}
						});
					},
					error: function() {
					}
				});
			}
			$('#btn-my-booking').removeClass('active');
		}

		$(document).ready(function () {
			$('#createAccountModalOpen').click(function (e) {
				GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'FE-3765', "Open Modal", "en", 1, true);
				createAccountModalOpen();
				e.preventDefault();
			});

			$("#createAccountModalClose").click(function () {
				GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'FE-3765', "Closed Modal", "en", 1, true);
				$("#modal_create_account").trigger("close");
			});

			$("#crmModalCreateEmail").bind('input', function () {
				$("#crmModalCreateEmail").removeClass("error");
				$("#crmModalCreateExists").hide();
				$("#crmModalCreateError").hide();
			});

			$("#crmModalCreatePass").bind('input', function () {
				$("#crmModalCreatePass").removeClass("error");
			});

			$("#crmModalCreateAccount").click(function () {
				var valid = true;
				if ($("#crmModalCreateEmail").val() === "") {
					$("#crmModalCreateEmail").addClass("error");
					valid = false;
				}
				if ($("#crmModalCreatePass").val() === "") {
					$("#crmModalCreatePass").addClass("error");
					valid = false;
				}
				if (valid) {
					$.ajax({
						type: "POST",
						data: {email: $("#crmModalCreateEmail").val()},
						url: '/CheckEmailRegistered.do;jsessionid=49CA5C96F09A7D6B27821F912D463145.node379a',
						cache: false,
						success: function (data) {
							if (data.emailRegistered) {
								// Email already exists on account.
								$("#crmModalCreateExists").show();
								$("#crmModalCreateEmail").addClass("error");
								GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'FE-3765', "Email already registered", "en", 1, true);
							} else {
								// Create account.
								$("#crmCreateEmail").val($("#crmModalCreateEmail").val());
								$("#crmCreatePsw").val($("#crmModalCreatePass").val());
								GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'FE-3765', "Created Account", "en", 1, true);
								GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'CRM Event', 'New CRM Account', $("#crmModalCreateEmail").val(), 1, true);
								GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'CRM Event', 'Loyalty entry', $("#crmModalCreateEmail").val(), 1, true);
								if (createAccount() === false) {
									$("#crmModalCreateEmail").addClass("error");
								}
							}
						}
					});
				}
			});
		});
	</script>

$(function(){
	/*** HEADER INTERACTION TRACKING ***/
	// Logo tracking
	$('.rch-logo-image, .logo-header').click(function(){
		GAQPushTransition("_trackEvent", "FE-2093", "rentalcars.com Logo", "Click", 1, true, '.rentalcars.com');
	});
	// Currency tracking
	$('#btn-currency, #rch-select-currency').click(function(){
		GAQPush("_trackEvent", "FE-2093", "Currency button", "Click", 1, true);
	});
	$('#btn-currency .dd-list ul li a, #rch-select-currency div ul li a').click(function(){
		GAQPushTransition("_trackEvent", "FE-2093", "Alternative currency selected: "+$(this).find('span').html(), "Click", 1, true, '.rentalcars.com');
	});
	// Language tracking
	$('#btn-language, #rch-select-language').click(function(){
		GAQPush("_trackEvent", "FE-2093", "Language button", "Click", 1, true);
	});
	$('#alternative-languages li a').click(function(){
		GAQPushTransition("_trackEvent", "FE-2093", "Alternative language selected: "+$(this).attr('id'), "Click", 1, true, '.rentalcars.com');
	});
	// My account tracking
	$('#btn-my-booking, #rch-select-sign-in').click(function(){
		GAQPush("_trackEvent", "FE-2093", "My account button", "Click", 1, true);
	});
});
</script>

						function saveQuotePopup(vehicleId, previousPrice, rateReference, locId, dropLocId, locName, dropLocName) {
							GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'FE-182', 'Quote button clicked', vehicleId, 1, true);

							var data = {};

							$('form[name="BookingExtrasForm"] input').each(function() {
								data[$(this).attr('name')] = $(this).val();
							});

							data['layout'] = 'quotePopup';
							data['previousPrice'] = previousPrice;
							data['vehicleInfo.vehicle.rateReference'] = rateReference;
							data['vehicleInfo.vehicle.id'] = vehicleId;
							data['vehicleInfo.supplier.locId'] = locId;
							data['vehicleInfo.supplier.dropLocId'] = dropLocId;
							data['locationName'] = locName;
							data['dropLocationName'] = dropLocName;
							data['location'] = locId;
							data['dropLocation'] = dropLocId;

							//Open the quote popup and set necessary information to fulfill the request
							$.ajax({
								url: "/RequestData.do",
								async: true,
								data: data,
								type: 'POST',
								success: function(data) {
									$('.quote-loading').hide();
									if($.trim(data) !== '') {
										$('<div/>').html(data)
												.lightbox_me({
													centered: true,
													closeClick: false,
													overlayCSS: {
														background: '#000',
														opacity: 0.4
													},
													fitInScreen: true,
													destroyOnClose: true,
													onLoad: function() {
														if(typeof assignQuoteValidationEvents != 'undefined') assignQuoteValidationEvents();
														
													}
												});
									}
									else {
										GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'FE-182', 'VehicleNotFound', '', 1, true);
									}
								},
								error: function(jqXHR, textStatus, errorThrown){
									GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'FE-182', 'quotePopupAjaxError', 'ajaxError', 1, true);
									if(jqXHR){
										var errorcode = 'ErrorCode:'+jqXHR.status;
										GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'FE-182', 'quotePopupAjaxErrorCode', errorcode, 1, true);
									}
								}
							});

						}

						function attachTooltipEvents(_this, message, classes) {
							$(_this).mouseover(function() {
								var messageTooltip = message;
								tooltipshow(_this,'', messageTooltip,undefined,undefined,{style:{classes: classes}});
							}).mouseout(function() {
								tooltipshow(_this);
							});
						}

						$(document).ready(function(){
							$('.carResultDiv [data-tooltip]').each(function(){
								var message = $(this).data('tooltip');
								var tooltipClass = $(this).data('tooltip-class');
								attachTooltipEvents($(this),message,tooltipClass);
							});

							$('.carResultRow_OfferInfo-btn-primary.animate').click(function(){
								$('.carResultRow_OfferInfo-btn-primary').removeClass('book-loading');
								$(this).addClass('book-loading');
							});

						});
					</script>

        var chineseLicenseInfo = ("To be eligible to hire a car in China, the driver must hold a valid driving licence issued by the People&#039;s Republic of China (Mainland). No other driving licences will be accepted, even when accompanied by an International Driving Permit (IDP).");

        function clickOnTheBox() {
            $('.ss_search_do_dropboxes').toggle();
          }

        var documentReadyChineese = function(){


            	$(".ss_search_pu_panel select[name='country'], .ss_search_do_dropboxes select[name='dropCountry']").bind("change", function(){
                    if ($(this).val() == "China") {
                         GAQPush("_trackEvent", "FE-5017", "DriverLicenceMessage", "", 1, true); 
                        $("#chinese-driver-license").show();
                        isChina = true;
                    } else {
                        $("#chinese-driver-license").hide();
                        isChina = false;
                    }
                });
                $("#topOfSearchForm").bind("submit", function(){
                    if (isChina && (!$("#chinese-license").is(":checked"))) {
                        alert(chineseLicenseInfo);
                        return false;
                    }
                });
				
                $('#show_return').click(function(){
                    clickOnTheBox();
                  });

                  $("#topOfSearchForm select[name=doHour]").val('10');
                  $("#topOfSearchForm select[name=doMinute]").val('0');
                }
                $("#topOfSearchForm").attr('action','SearchResults.do');
                var emptySearchResultsObject = $('#topOfSearchForm').find('[name=emptySearchResults]');
                if (emptySearchResultsObject.length == 0){
                  $('#topOfSearchForm').append('<input type="hidden" name="emptySearchResults" value="false" />');
                }else{
                  emptySearchResultsObject.attr('value','false');
                }
                $('#topOfSearchForm').submit();
              });

            }

        function setPuDate(date)
        {
            if( getDoDate() < date ) {
                setDoDate(date);
            }

            var month = date.getMonth()+1;
            
            if( date.getMonth() != getPuDate(true).getMonth() || date.getFullYear() != getPuDate(true).getFullYear() ) {
                $('#puMonth_select').val(month+"-"+date.getFullYear());
                var updateDays = true;
                setPuDisplayDate(updateDays, date);
            }

            if(date.getDate() != getPuDate(true).getDate()) {
                $('#puDay_select').val(date.getDate());
            }
            

        }

        function setPuDisplayDate(updateDays, date)
        {
            var year = date.getFullYear();
            var month = parseInt(date.getMonth()) + 1;
            var day = $('#puDay_select').val();

            if( updateDays ) {

                var foundDay = false;

                var firstDay = 1;
                var lastDay = 32 - new Date( year, month-1, 32 ).getDate();

                $('#puDay_select option').remove();
                $('#puDay_select').append('<option value="-1" disabled="disabled">' + dayTxt + '</option>');

                var nextDay = new Date( year, month-1, 1 );
                for(var i=firstDay; i<=lastDay; i++) {
                    nextDay.setDate(i);
                    var formattedDate = $.datepicker.formatDate('D d', nextDay, {dayNamesShort: dayNamesShort});
                    $('#puDay_select').append('<option value="' + i + '">' + formattedDate + '</option>');
                    if(i==day) foundDay = true;
                }

                if(foundDay) {
                    $('#puDay_select').val(day);
                    
                } else {
                    $('input[name=puDay]').val( $('#puDay_select').val() );
                }

            } else {
                $('#puDay_select').val(day);
                
            }
        }

        function setDoDate(date)
        {
            var month = date.getMonth()+1;

            
            if( date.getMonth() != getDoDate(true).getMonth() || date.getFullYear() != getDoDate(true).getFullYear() ) {
                $('#doMonth_select').val(month+"-"+date.getFullYear());
                var updateDays = true;
                setDoDisplayDate(updateDays, date);
            }

            if(date.getDate() != getDoDate(true).getDate()) {
                $('#doDay_select').val(date.getDate());
            }
            
        }

        function setDoDisplayDate(updateDays, date)
        {
            var year = date.getFullYear();
            var month = parseInt(date.getMonth()) + 1;
            var day = $('#doDay_select').val();

            if( updateDays ) {

                var foundDay = false;

                var firstDay = 1;
                var lastDay = 32 - new Date( year, month-1, 32 ).getDate();

                $('#doDay_select option').remove();
                $('#doDay_select').append('<option value="-1" disabled="disabled">' + dayTxt + '</option>');

                var nextDay = new Date( year, month-1, 1 );
                for(var i=firstDay; i<=lastDay; i++) {
                    nextDay.setDate(i);
                    var formattedDate = $.datepicker.formatDate('D d', nextDay, {dayNamesShort: dayNamesShort});
                    $('#doDay_select').append('<option value="' + i + '">' + formattedDate + '</option>');
                    if(i==day) foundDay = true;
                }

                if(foundDay) {
                    $('#doDay_select').val(day);
                    
                } else {
                    $('input[name=doDay]').val( $('#doDay_select').val() );
                    
                }

            } else {
                $('#doDay_select').val(day);
                
            }
        }

        function getPuDate(daychange)
        {
            var returnValue = null;

            var puMonthYearObjectExists = false;
            var puMonthYearObject = $('select[name="puMonthYear"]');
            if(typeof puMonthYearObject != 'undefined')
            {
                var puMonthYear = puMonthYearObject.val();
                if(typeof puMonthYear != 'undefined' && puMonthYear != "") {
                    puMonthYearObjectExists = true;
                }
            }

            if(puMonthYearObjectExists && typeof daychange === 'undefined')
            {
                var value = puMonthYearObject.val().split('-');
                returnValue = new Date ( parseInt(value[1]),
                parseInt(value[0])-1,
                parseInt($('#puDay_select').val()));
            }
            else if( $('input[name=puYear]').val() != '' && $('input[name=puMonth]').val() != '' && $('input[name=puDay]').val() != '' ) {
                returnValue = new Date ( parseInt($('input[name=puYear]').val()),
                    parseInt($('input[name=puMonth]').val())-1,
                    parseInt($('input[name=puDay]').val()) );
            } else {
                returnValue = new Date ( today.getFullYear(),
                    today.getMonth(),
                    today.getDate() + 2);
                $('input[name=puDay]').val( returnValue.getDate() );
                $('input[name=puMonth]').val( returnValue.getMonth() + 1 );
                $('input[name=puYear]').val( returnValue.getFullYear() );
            }
            return returnValue;
        }

        function getDoDate(daychange)
        {
            var returnValue = null;

            var doMonthYearObjectExists = false;
            var doMonthYearObject = $('select[name="doMonthYear"]');
            if(typeof doMonthYearObject != 'undefined')
            {
                var doMonthYear = doMonthYearObject.val();
                if(typeof doMonthYear != 'undefined' && doMonthYear != "") {
                    doMonthYearObjectExists = true;
                }
            }

            if(doMonthYearObjectExists && typeof daychange === 'undefined')
            {
                var value = doMonthYearObject.val().split('-');
                returnValue = new Date ( parseInt(value[1]),
                parseInt(value[0])-1,
                parseInt($('#doDay_select').val()));
            }
            else if( $('input[name=doYear]').val() != '' && $('input[name=doMonth]').val() != '' && $('input[name=doDay]').val() != '' ) {
                returnValue = new Date ( parseInt($('input[name=doYear]').val()),
                    parseInt($('input[name=doMonth]').val())-1,
                    parseInt($('input[name=doDay]').val()) );
            } else {
                returnValue = new Date ( today.getFullYear(),
                    today.getMonth(),
                    today.getDate() + 4);
                $('input[name=doDay]').val( returnValue.getDate() );
                $('input[name=doMonth]').val( returnValue.getMonth() + 1 );
                $('input[name=doYear]').val( returnValue.getFullYear() );
            }
            return returnValue;
        }

			var incleaseNumCars = function() {
				$('#proceed .proceed-btn').unbind('click');

				
				$('#proceed .proceed-btn').click(searchAgainFormSubmit);
					
			};

			
	        		$(document).ready(incleaseNumCars);
	        	

			function searchAgainFormSubmit() {
				if (validateBeforeSearchResultsSubmission()) {
					if ($('#show_return').attr('checked') == true) {
						$(droplists).each(function(index, value) {
							if (index > 2) {
								$(droplists[index].jqSelector).empty().append($(droplists[index - 3].jqSelector).find('option:selected').clone()).attr('disabled', false);
							}
						});
					}
					$('input[name=locationName]').val($(droplists[2].jqSelector).find('option:selected').html());
					$('input[name=dropLocationName]').val($(droplists[5].jqSelector).find('option:selected').html());
					if ($(droplists[2].jqSelector).val() == -1 && $(droplists[5].jqSelector).val() == -1) {
						if ($(droplists[0].jqSelector).val() == $(droplists[3].jqSelector).val() && $(droplists[1].jqSelector).val() == $(droplists[4].jqSelector).val()) {
							$('#topOfSearchForm input[name=searchType]').val('allareasgeosearch');

									$('#topOfSearchForm input[name=filterFrom]').val('0');
									$('form[name=SearchResultsForm] input[name=filterTo]').val('49');


						} else {
							$('#topOfSearchForm input[name=searchType]').val('manytomanysearch');
							$('#topOfSearchForm input[name=filterFrom]').val('0');
							$('#topOfSearchForm input[name=filterTo]').val('20');
						}
					} else if ($(droplists[2].jqSelector).val() == -1 && $(droplists[5].jqSelector).val() != -1) {
						$('#topOfSearchForm input[name=searchType]').val('manytoonesearch');
						$('#topOfSearchForm input[name=filterFrom]').val('0');
						$('#topOfSearchForm input[name=filterTo]').val('20');
					} else if ($(droplists[2].jqSelector).val() != -1 && $(droplists[5].jqSelector).val() == -1) {
						$('#topOfSearchForm input[name=searchType]').val('onetomanysearch');
						$('#topOfSearchForm input[name=filterFrom]').val('0');
						$('#topOfSearchForm input[name=filterTo]').val('20');
					} else {
						$('#topOfSearchForm input[name=searchType]').val('');
						$('#topOfSearchForm input[name=filterFrom]').val('0');
						$('#topOfSearchForm input[name=filterTo]').val('1000');
					}
					var puMonthYearObject = $('select[name="puMonthYear"]');
					if (typeof puMonthYearObject != 'undefined') {
						var puMonthYear = puMonthYearObject.val();
						if (typeof puMonthYear != 'undefined' && puMonthYear != "") {
							var value = puMonthYear.split('-');
							if (value[0] != 'undefined') {
								$('input[name=puMonth]').val(value[0]);
							}
							if (value[1] != 'undefined') {
								$('input[name=puYear]').val(value[1]);
							}
						}
					}
					var doMonthYearObject = $('select[name="doMonthYear"]');
					if (typeof doMonthYearObject != 'undefined') {
						var doMonthYear = doMonthYearObject.val();
						if (typeof doMonthYear != 'undefined' && doMonthYear != "") {
							var value = doMonthYear.split('-');
							if (value[0] != 'undefined') {
								$('input[name=doMonth]').val(value[0]);
							}
							if (value[1] != 'undefined') {
								$('input[name=doYear]').val(value[1]);
							}
						}
					}
					saveInput();
					$('#topOfSearchForm').submit();
				}

			}
		</script>

        //Get a list of options selected, using checkboxes, within the specified jQuery selector
        function getCheckboxParamValue(container) {          
            var checkedValues = [];
            $("input:checkbox", $(container)).each(function() {               
                  if($(this).is(":checked") == true)
                    checkedValues.push($(this).val());
            });
            return checkedValues.join(':');
        }

  
  //Attach regular toggle and filter events to all checkboxes in a specific selector
  //If "includeParametersWhenAllSelected" is true, all values from checkboxes will be taken even if they are all selected
  function attachCheckboxEvents(selector, paramName, logLabel, includeParametersWhenAllSelected) {
    var checkboxes = $('input:checkbox', $(selector));

    //Attach filter event
    checkboxes.bind('filter', function() {
        if ($(this).parent().attr('num') != 0){
            $('form[name="ComplexFiltersForm"]').submit(function() {
                fillInFilterInputValue(paramName, getCheckboxParamValue(selector, includeParametersWhenAllSelected));
            });
            submitForm(this);
        }
    });
    
    //Toggle input state without triggering event
    checkboxes.bind('toggle', function() {
        $(this).attr('checked', !$(this).is(':checked'));
    });
    
    //Attach click event
    checkboxes.click(function() {
          try {
            GAQPushTransition('_trackEvent', 'SearchResultsFilters', logLabel, getCheckboxParamValue(selector, includeParametersWhenAllSelected), 1, true);
          } catch (err) {}
          
          $(this).trigger('filter');
    });
  }
  
  function submitForm(obj) {
      if(submitTimeout!=null)
            clearTimeout(submitTimeout);
      
          submitTimeout = setTimeout(function() {
            fillInFilterInputValue("filterAdditionalInfo",getAdditionalInfoParamValue());
            fillInFilterInputValue("advSearch",getAdvSearchParamValue());
            fillInFilterInputValue("exSuppliers",getExSuppliersValues());
			
            
            $("form[name=ComplexFiltersForm]").submit();
          }, 0);
  }

</script>

	</span><script type="text/javascript" nonce="q9qsq10594e1qf6gbpc6lfj6ss">
	    	var tempJqueryVar = jQuery;
	    	jQuery = jQuery171;
	    </script>
	    <script type="text/javascript" src="/js/jcarousel-0.3.0.js"></script>
    <script nonce="q9qsq10594e1qf6gbpc6lfj6ss">
	        
	        	jQuery = tempJqueryVar;
	        
	        
	        //Common carousel functions
	        function carouselScrollControlToggle(control, appearCondition) {
	            if(appearCondition) {
	                jQuery171(control).removeClass('disabled').removeClass('invisible');
	            }
	            else {
	                //Avoid unwanted clicks on categories when scrolling by changing background to later not display it at all
	                jQuery171(control).addClass('invisible');
	                setTimeout(function() {
	                    if(jQuery171(control).hasClass('invisible')) {
	                        jQuery171(control).addClass('disabled').removeClass('invisible');
	                    }
	                }, 800);
	            }
	        }
	        
	        //Activates/deactivates scroll controls on carousel
	        function carouselScrollControlCheckBounds(carousel, visibleNumberItems) {
	            carouselScrollControlToggle(
	                carousel.siblings('.arrow-left'),
	                jQuery171.inArray(carousel.jcarousel('items')[0], carousel.jcarousel('fullyvisible')) < 0
	            );
	            carouselScrollControlToggle(
	                carousel.siblings('.arrow-right'),
	                jQuery171.inArray(carousel.jcarousel('items')[carousel.jcarousel('items').length-1], carousel.jcarousel('fullyvisible')) < 0
	            );
	        };

            function updateHiddenFormParameter(name, value) {
                var forms = $('form');
                $('form').each(function() {
                    var input = $('input[type="hidden"][name="'+name+'"]', this);
                    if(input.length == 0) {
                        input = $('<input/>').attr({ type: 'hidden', name: name, value: value});
                        $(this).append(input);
                    }
                    else {
                        input.val(value);
                    }
                });
            }
            
            $('.showLocationTabsMapLink').click(function() {
                GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'SearchResultsFilters', 'showMapLocationFilter', 'Show all areas', 1, true);
                showDualMap();
                return false; //Prevent bubbling
            });
            
            $('.refine_by_filter .refine_by_list > li > a:not(.showLocationTabsMapLink)').click(function() {
            	
	                $('.refine_by_filter .refine_by_list li a').removeClass('refined_highlight');
                    $(this).addClass('refined_highlight');
                    
                    GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'SearchResultsFilters', 'refineBy', $(this).hasClass('carTypeRefine') ? 'carclass' : 'location', 1, true);
                    if($(this).closest('.refine_by_list').is('.refine_filter_type')) {
                        
                        //toggle between car categories carousel and location carousel
                        if($(this).hasClass('carTypeRefine')) {
                            updateHiddenFormParameter('refineBy', 'carclass');
                            showCategoriesCarousel();
                            hideLocationCarousel();
                        }
                        else{
                            showLocationCarousel();
                            
                                //reload location carousel as has not been shown since the beginning
                                jQuery171('#all_areas_scroll_carousel').jcarousel('reload', { list: 'ul', items: '> li:visible' });
                            
                            hideCategoriesCarousel();
                            
                            var value;
                            
                            if($(this).hasClass('airportLocationType')) {
                                value = 'airport';
                            }
                            else if($(this).hasClass('stationLocationType')) {
                                value = 'station';
                            }
                            else if($(this).hasClass('otherLocationType')) {
                                value = 'other';
                            }
                            else {
                                value = 'all';
                            }
                            
                            GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'SearchResultsFilters', 'refineLocationType', value, 1, true);
                            
                            var locationTabs = $('#all_areas_scroll_carousel > ul > li');
                            if(value == 'all') {
                                locationTabs.show();
                            }
                            else {
                                locationTabsToRemove = locationTabs.filter(function() {
                                    return !$(this).hasClass('loc_type_'+value);
                                });
                                locationTabsToRemove.hide();
                                locationTabs.not(locationTabsToRemove).show();
                            }
                            //reload carousel, as items have changed
                            jQuery171('#all_areas_scroll_carousel').jcarousel('reload', { list: 'ul', items: '> li:visible' });
                            //Jump to the first one, with no animation
                            jQuery171('#all_areas_scroll_carousel').jcarousel('scroll', 0, false);
                            
                            
                            updateHiddenFormParameter('refineLocType', value);
                        }
                    }
            });
            $(document).data('all_areas_location_data', []);
        </script>

        <script nonce="q9qsq10594e1qf6gbpc6lfj6ss">
            function hideLocationCarousel() {
                $('#all_areas_scroll').hide();
            }
            
            function showLocationCarousel() {
                //Show carousel already, as we need to set the height of the tabs properly
                $('#all_areas_scroll').show();
                
                //Show "refine by location" filter, if exists
                $('.refine_by_location_options').show();
                
                if(!$('#all_areas_scroll').data('loaded')) {
                    $('#all_areas_scroll').data('loaded', true);
                    
                    //Set location tabs height dinamically to be the same and adapt as needed
                    $('#all_areas_scroll').data('higherHeight', 0);
                    $('.all_area_tab').each(function() {
                        var thisHeight = $(this).height();
                        if(thisHeight > $('#all_areas_scroll').data('higherHeight')) {
                            $('#all_areas_scroll').data('higherHeight', thisHeight);
                        }
                    });
                    
                    $('.all_area_tab:not(.all_area_alloptions)').css('height', $('#all_areas_scroll').data('higherHeight')+'px');
                    $('.all_area_tab .all_area_tab_allcarstxt').css('height', $('#all_areas_scroll').data('higherHeight')+'px');
                    
//                     //Scroll carousel to selected location (only if it's not visible)
//                     if($('.all_area_tab').index($('.tab_selected_area')) > 5 && typeof jQuery171('#all_areas_scroll_carousel').data('jcarousel') !== 'undefined') {
//                         jQuery171('#all_areas_scroll_carousel').jcarousel('scroll', jQuery171('.all_area_tab.tab_selected_area'), false);
//                     }
                }
            }
            
            $('.all_area_tab').click(function() {
                if($(this).is('.all_area_alloptions')) {
                    if($(this).is(':not(.tab_selected_area)')) {
                        GAQPushTransition('_trackEvent', 'SearchResultsFilters', 'allAreasFilter_chosen', 'all_locations', 1, true);
                        //Default to "all" in the loc type
                        updateHiddenFormParameter('refineLocType', 'all');
                        updateHiddenFormParameter('refineBy', 'location');
                        $(this).trigger('filter_cars');
                    }
                }
                else {
                    try {
                        GAQPushTransition('_trackEvent', 'SearchResultsFilters',
                                $(this).hasClass('tab_selected_area') ? 'allAreasFilter_deselect' : 'allAreasFilter_chosen', //label
                                $('.locationData > .locationType', this).text(), //value
                                1, true);
                    }
                    catch(e) {}
                    updateHiddenFormParameter('refineBy', 'location');
                    $(this).trigger('filter_cars');
                }
            });
            
            
            
            //Initialize carousel
            jQuery171('#all_areas_scroll_carousel')
                .on('jcarousel:scrollend jcarousel:createend jcarousel:reloadend', function() {
                    //Hide/show scroll controls every time we scroll
                    carouselScrollControlCheckBounds(jQuery171(this), 6);
                })
                .jcarousel({ animation: 'slow', vertical: false, list: 'ul', items: '> li:visible' });
            
            //Initialize carousel controls
            jQuery171('#all_areas_scroll .arrow-left').jcarouselControl({ target: '-=5' });
            jQuery171('#all_areas_scroll .arrow-right').jcarouselControl({ target: '+=5' });
            
            if($('.small_screen_size_check').css('display') == 'block'){
		        	//Scroll carousel to selected location (only if it's not visible)
		            if($('.all_area_tab').index($('.tab_selected_area')) > 5) {
		                jQuery171('#all_areas_scroll_carousel').jcarousel('scroll', jQuery171('.all_area_tab.tab_selected_area').prev(), false);
		            }
            }
		    else{
		        	//Scroll carousel to selected location (only if it's not visible)
		            if($('.all_area_tab').index($('.tab_selected_area')) > 6) {
		                jQuery171('#all_areas_scroll_carousel').jcarousel('scroll', jQuery171('.all_area_tab.tab_selected_area').prev(), false);
		            }
		    }
            
            
            
            /* Location filtering */
            $('.all_area_alloptions').bind('filter_cars', function() {
                //Do nothing if the "all cars" category is already selected
                if(!$(this).hasClass('tab_selected_area')) {
                    //deselect current category and select "all cars" category
                    $('#all_areas_scroll .all_area_alloptions.tab_selected_area').removeClass('tab_selected_area');
                    $(this).addClass('tab_selected_area');
                    
                    $("#all_areas_location_loading").show();
                    
                    var form = $('form[name="ComplexFiltersForm"]');
                    $('input[name="filterCoordinates"]', form).remove();
                    submitForm();
                }
            });
            
            $('.all_area_tab:not(.all_area_alloptions)').bind('filter_cars', function() {
                if($(this).hasClass('tab_selected_area')) {
                    //Category unselected, show all cars
                    $('.all_area_alloptions').trigger('filter_cars');
                }
                else {
                	updateHiddenFormParameter('refineLocType', 'all');
                    updateHiddenFormParameter('refineBy', 'location');
                    //filter cars by category
                    $('#all_areas_scroll .all_area_tab.tab_selected_area').removeClass('tab_selected_area');
                    $(this).addClass('tab_selected_area');
                    
                    $("#all_areas_location_loading").show();
                    
                    var form = $('form[name="ComplexFiltersForm"]');
                    var input = $('input[name="filterCoordinates"]', form);
                    if(input.length == 0) {
                        input = $('<input/>').attr({
                            type: 'hidden',
                            name: 'filterCoordinates' 
                        });
                        form.append(input);
                    }
                    input.val($('.locationData > .coordinates', this).text());
                    submitForm();
                }
            });
            
            </script>

        //Initialize carousel
        jQuery171('#car_cat_scroll_carousel')
            .on('jcarousel:scrollend', function() {
                //Hide/show scroll controls every time we scroll
                carouselScrollControlCheckBounds(jQuery171(this), 5);
            })
            .jcarousel({ animation: 'slow', vertical: false });
            
        
        //Initialize carousel controls
        jQuery171('#car_cat_scroll .arrow-left').jcarouselControl({ target: '-=4' });
        jQuery171('#car_cat_scroll .arrow-right').jcarouselControl({ target: '+=4' });
        
        /* Car category filtering */
        $('.car_cat_all_cars_tab').bind('filter_cars', function() {
            //Do nothing if the "all cars" category is already selected
            if(!$(this).hasClass('car_cat_tab_chosen')) {
                //deselect current category and select "all cars" category
                $('#car_cat_scroll .car_cat_tab.car_cat_tab_chosen').removeClass('car_cat_tab_chosen');
                $(this).addClass('car_cat_tab_chosen');
                
                $("#car_cat_loading").show();
                
                var form = $('form[name="ComplexFiltersForm"]');
                $('input[name="filter_carclass"]', form).remove();
                $.cookies.set('srvi', 'filter-carclass-allcars');
                submitForm();
            }
        });
        
        
		        $('.car_cat_tab:not(.car_cat_all_cars_tab)').bind('filter_cars', function() {
		            if($(this).hasClass('car_cat_tab_chosen')) {
		                //Category unselected, show all cars
		                $('.car_cat_all_cars_tab').trigger('filter_cars');
		            }
		            else {
		                //filter cars by category
		                $('#car_cat_scroll .car_cat_tab.car_cat_tab_chosen').removeClass('car_cat_tab_chosen');
		                $(this).addClass('car_cat_tab_chosen');
		                
		                $("#car_cat_loading").show();
		                
		                var form = $('form[name="ComplexFiltersForm"]');
		                var input = $('input[name="filter_carclass"]', form);
		                if(input.length == 0) {
		                    input = $('<input/>').attr({
		                        type: 'hidden',
		                        name: 'filter_carclass' 
		                    });
		                    form.append(input);
		                }
		                
			            input.val($('.carCategoryData > .normalizedName', this).text());
			            $.cookies.set('srvi', 'filter-carclass');
		                submitForm();
		            }
		        });
			
        
        
        function hideCategoriesCarousel() {
            $('#car_cat_scroll').hide();
        }
        function showCategoriesCarousel() {
        	
            //Show car categorization after being created
            $('#car_cat_scroll').show();
            //Hide "refine by location" filter, if exists
            hideLocationCarousel();
            
            if(!$('#car_cat_scroll').data('loaded')) {
                $('#car_cat_scroll').data('loaded', true);
                
                $('.car_cat_tab').click(function() {
                    if($(this).is('.car_cat_all_cars_tab')) {
                        if($(this).is(':not(.car_cat_tab_chosen)')) {
                            GAQPushTransition('_trackEvent', 'SearchResultsFilters', 'categoryFilter_chosen', 'all_cars', 1, true);
                            $(this).trigger('filter_cars');
                        }
                    }
                    else {
                        try {
                            GAQPushTransition('_trackEvent', 'SearchResultsFilters',
                                    $(this).hasClass('car_cat_tab_chosen') ? 'categoryFilter_deselect' : 'categoryFilter_chosen', //label
                                    $('.carCategoryData > .normalizedName', this).text(), //value
                                    1, true);
                        }
                        catch(e) {}
                        
                        $(this).trigger('filter_cars');
                    }
                });
                
                if($('.small_screen_size_check').css('display') == 'block'){
			        	//Scroll carousel to selected category (only if it's not visible)
		                if($('.car_cat_tab').index($('.car_cat_tab_chosen')) > 4) {
		                    //No sliding effect
		                    jQuery171('#car_cat_scroll_carousel').jcarousel('scroll', jQuery171('.car_cat_tab.car_cat_tab_chosen').prev(), false);
		                }
		                else{
		                	jQuery171('#car_cat_scroll_carousel').jcarousel('scroll', 0, false);//It fixes the scoll to end bug
		                }
                }
                else{
			        	//Scroll carousel to selected category (only if it's not visible)
		                if($('.car_cat_tab').index($('.car_cat_tab_chosen')) > 5) {
		                    //No sliding effect
		                    jQuery171('#car_cat_scroll_carousel').jcarousel('scroll', jQuery171('.car_cat_tab.car_cat_tab_chosen').prev(), false);
		                }
		                else{
		                	jQuery171('#car_cat_scroll_carousel').jcarousel('scroll', 0, false);//It fixes the scoll to end bug
		                }
                }
                
                
                //Set car category tabs height dinamically to be the same and adapt as needed
                
                var catNameHeight = 16;
                $('.car_cat_tab div.selectable-item span.t').each(function() {
                    var thisHeight = $(this).height();
                    if(thisHeight > catNameHeight) {
                    	catNameHeight = thisHeight;
                    }
                });
                
                $('.car_cat_tab div.selectable-item span.t').css('height', catNameHeight+'px');
                

	                    var catHeight = 140;

                $('.car_cat_tab div.selectable-item').each(function() {
                    var thisHeight = $(this).height();
                    if(thisHeight > catHeight) {
                    	catHeight = thisHeight;
                    }
                });
                
                $('.car_cat_tab div.selectable-item').css('height', catHeight+'px');
                
            }
        }
        
            showCategoriesCarousel();
        </script>

		  var puLocations = new Array();
		  var doLocations = new Array();
		  
		  $(function() {

		  var puMapOpts = { center: new google.maps.LatLng(0,0), zoom: 13, disableDefaultUI: true, panControl: true, zoomControl: true, mapTypeControl: false, scaleControl: false, streetViewControl: false, overviewMapControl: false, mapTypeId: google.maps.MapTypeId.ROADMAP };
		  var doMapOpts = { center: new google.maps.LatLng(0,0), zoom: 13, disableDefaultUI: true, panControl: true, zoomControl: true, mapTypeControl: false, scaleControl: false, streetViewControl: false, overviewMapControl: false, mapTypeId: google.maps.MapTypeId.ROADMAP };
		
		  var pickupMap = null;
		    var dropoffMap = null;  
		  
		    var puSearchMarker = null;
		    var doSearchMarker = null;
		    
		  var puMarkers = new Array();
		  var doMarkers = new Array();
		    
		    var redIcon = "http://cdn.rcstatic.com/images/site_graphics/newsite/map_pointer.png";
		    var blueIcon = "http://cdn.rcstatic.com/images/site_graphics/newsite/pin-car-b.png";
		    var blueAirportIcon = "http://cdn.rcstatic.com/images/site_graphics/newsite/pin-airport-b.png";
		
		  
		  function showDualMap() {
		// 	$('.all_areas_filter_map').click(function() {
		      $('#all_areas_location_filter_map').lightbox_me({ centered: true, 
		        onLoad: function() {
		          if(pickupMap==null && dropoffMap==null) {
		            initPuMap();
		              initDoMap();
		              initPuMarkers();
		              initDoMarkers();
		              centerPuMap();centerDoMap();
		//               initPuSearchMarker();
		//               initDoSearchMarker();
		              initEventsForA2A();
		          } else {
		            google.maps.event.trigger(pickupMap, 'resize');
		            google.maps.event.trigger(dropoffMap, 'resize');  
		          }
		        } 
		      }); 
		//     });

		  }
		  
		  function initDropdownAnimationEvents() {
		    $(".pu_dd_trigger").click(function() {
		      $(".pu_dd").slideToggle();
		      $(".do_dd").slideUp();
		    });
		    
		    $(".do_dd_trigger").click(function(e) {
		      $(".do_dd").slideToggle();
		      $(".pu_dd").slideUp();
		    });
		    
		    $("html").click(function() {
		      $(".pu_dd").slideUp();
		      $(".do_dd").slideUp();
		    });
		    $(".location-dropdown-popup").click(function(){
		    	$(this).parents('.filter_content').addClass('reload');
			   	filterToggle = $(this).parents('.filter_container').find('.filter_toggle');
			   	filterToggle.addClass('reload');
		    });
		    $(".location-dropdown-popup,.pu_dd_trigger,.do_dd_trigger").click(function(e){
		      	e.stopPropagation();
		    });
		  }
		  
		  function initFilteringEvents() {
		    $(".pu_filter_link").click(function() {
		      
		      if( $("form[name=ComplexFiltersForm] input[name=filterCoordinates]").length == 0 ) {
		        $("form[name=ComplexFiltersForm]").append(
		          $(document.createElement("input"))
		            .attr("type","hidden")
		            .attr("name","filterCoordinates")
		          );
		      }
		      $('form[name=ComplexFiltersForm] input[name=filterCoordinates]').val($(this).attr("coordinates"));
		      $('form[name=ComplexFiltersForm] input[name=filterFrom]').val(0);        
		      $('form[name=ComplexFiltersForm] input[name=filterTo]').val(20);
		      $(".pu_dd").hide();
		      submitForm();
		    });
		    
		    $(".do_filter_link").click(function() {
		      if( $("form[name=ComplexFiltersForm] input[name=filterDropCoordinates]").length == 0 ) {
		        $("form[name=ComplexFiltersForm]").append(
		          $(document.createElement("input"))
		            .attr("type","hidden")
		            .attr("name","filterDropCoordinates")
		          );
		      }
		      $('form[name=ComplexFiltersForm] input[name=filterDropCoordinates]').val($(this).attr("coordinates"));
		      $('form[name=ComplexFiltersForm] input[name=filterFrom]').val(0);        
		      $('form[name=ComplexFiltersForm] input[name=filterTo]').val(20);
		      $(".do_dd").hide();
		      submitForm();   
		    });
		  }
		  
		  function initPuMap() {
		    pickupMap = new google.maps.Map(document.getElementById("pickupMap"), puMapOpts);
		  }
		  
		  function initDoMap() {
		    dropoffMap = new google.maps.Map(document.getElementById("dropoffMap"), doMapOpts);
		  }
		  
		  function initPuMarkers() {
		    $(puLocations).each(function() {
		      puMarkers.push(
		        new google.maps.Marker({
		          position: new google.maps.LatLng(this.latitude,this.longitude),
		          map: pickupMap,
		              title: this.name,
		              icon:this.name.toLowerCase().indexOf('airport'.toLowerCase()) < 0 ? blueIcon : blueAirportIcon })
		        );
		      });   
		  }
		  
		  function initDoMarkers() {
		    $(doLocations).each(function() {
		      doMarkers.push(
		        new google.maps.Marker({
		          position: new google.maps.LatLng(this.latitude,this.longitude),
		          map: dropoffMap,
		              title: this.name,
		              icon:this.name.toLowerCase().indexOf('airport'.toLowerCase()) < 0 ? blueIcon : blueAirportIcon})
		        );
		    });
		  }
		  
		  function centerPuMap() {
		    google.maps.event.addListenerOnce(pickupMap, 'zoom_changed', function() { if( pickupMap.getZoom() > 12 ) pickupMap.setZoom(12); });   
		    bounds = new google.maps.LatLngBounds();
		    $(puMarkers).each(function() { 
		      bounds.extend( this.getPosition() );  
		    });     
		      pickupMap.fitBounds(bounds);
		    }
		  
		  function centerDoMap() {
		    google.maps.event.addListenerOnce(dropoffMap, 'zoom_changed', function() { if( dropoffMap.getZoom() > 12 ) dropoffMap.setZoom(12); });
		      bounds = new google.maps.LatLngBounds();
		    $(doMarkers).each(function() { 
		      bounds.extend( this.getPosition() );  
		    });     
		    dropoffMap.fitBounds(bounds);
		  }
		    
		  function initPuSearchMarker() {
		    
		      var puMarkersBounds  = new google.maps.LatLngBounds();
		      $(puMarkers).each(function() { 
		        puMarkersBounds.extend( this.getPosition() ); 
		      });     
		      puSearchMarker = new google.maps.Marker({
		          position: puMarkersBounds.getCenter(),
		          map: pickupMap,
		            title: "search centre",
		            icon: redIcon,
		            draggable: true });
		    
		  }
		    
		  function initDoSearchMarker() {
		    
		      var doMarkersBounds  = new google.maps.LatLngBounds();
		      $(doMarkers).each(function() { 
		        doMarkersBounds.extend( this.getPosition() ); 
		      });     
		      doSearchMarker = new google.maps.Marker({
		        position: doMarkersBounds.getCenter(),
		        map: dropoffMap,
		          title: "search centre",
		          icon: redIcon,
		          draggable: true });
		    
		  }
		  
		  function initPuDrawingManager() {
		    var puDrawingManager = new google.maps.drawing.DrawingManager({   
		      drawingControl: true,
		      drawingControlOptions: {
		        position: google.maps.ControlPosition.TOP_RIGHT,
		        drawingModes: [google.maps.drawing.OverlayType.MARKER]      
		      },
		      markerOptions: {
		        icon: redIcon,
		        draggable: true
		      }
		    });
		    
		    puDrawingManager.setMap(pickupMap);
		    
		    google.maps.event.addListener(puDrawingManager, 'markercomplete', function(marker) {
		      if(puSearchMarker!=null) {
		        puSearchMarker.setMap(null);
		      }
		      puSearchMarker = marker;      
		    });
		  }
		  
		  function initDoDrawingManager() {
		    var doDrawingManager = new google.maps.drawing.DrawingManager({   
		      drawingControl: true,
		      drawingControlOptions: {
		        position: google.maps.ControlPosition.TOP_RIGHT,
		        drawingModes: [google.maps.drawing.OverlayType.MARKER]      
		      },
		      markerOptions: {
		        icon: redIcon,
		        draggable: true
		      }
		    });
		    
		    doDrawingManager.setMap(dropoffMap);
		    
		    google.maps.event.addListener(doDrawingManager, 'markercomplete', function(marker) {
		      if(doSearchMarker!=null) {
		        doSearchMarker.setMap(null);
		      }
		      doSearchMarker = marker;      
		    });
		  }
		
		  function initEventsForA2A() {
		    $('.coordinates_search_link').click(function() {
		      
		      if(puSearchMarker!=null && doSearchMarker!=null) {
		        
		        
		        if( $("form[name=ComplexFiltersForm] input[name=longitude]").length == 0 ) {
		          $("form[name=ComplexFiltersForm]").append(
		            $(document.createElement("input"))
		              .attr("type","hidden")
		              .attr("name","longitude")
		          );
		        }
		        
		        if( $("form[name=ComplexFiltersForm] input[name=latitude]").length == 0 ) {
		          $("form[name=ComplexFiltersForm]").append(
		            $(document.createElement("input"))
		              .attr("type","hidden")
		              .attr("name","latitude")
		            );
		        }
		        
		        if( $("form[name=ComplexFiltersForm] input[name=dropLongitude]").length == 0 ) {
		          $("form[name=ComplexFiltersForm]").append(
		            $(document.createElement("input"))
		              .attr("type","hidden")
		              .attr("name","dropLongitude")
		            );
		        }
		            
		        if( $("form[name=ComplexFiltersForm] input[name=dropLatitude]").length == 0 ) {
		          $("form[name=ComplexFiltersForm]").append(
		            $(document.createElement("input"))
		              .attr("type","hidden")
		              .attr("name","dropLatitude")
		            );
		        }
		        
		        if( $("form[name=ComplexFiltersForm] input[name=emptySearchResults]").length == 0 ) {
		          $("form[name=ComplexFiltersForm]").append( 
		            $(document.createElement("input"))
		              .attr("type","hidden")
		              .attr("name","emptySearchResults")              
		            );
		        }
		                        
		        $('form[name=ComplexFiltersForm]').attr("action","/LoadingSearchResults.do");
		        
		        $("form[name=ComplexFiltersForm]").find("input[name=emptySearchResults]").val("true");
		                
		        $("form[name=ComplexFiltersForm]").find("input[name=longitude]").val(puSearchMarker.getPosition().lng());
		        $("form[name=ComplexFiltersForm]").find("input[name=latitude]").val(puSearchMarker.getPosition().lat());
		        $("form[name=ComplexFiltersForm]").find("input[name=dropLongitude]").val(doSearchMarker.getPosition().lng());
		        $("form[name=ComplexFiltersForm]").find("input[name=dropLatitude]").val(doSearchMarker.getPosition().lat());
		        
		        $("form[name=ComplexFiltersForm]").find("input[name=filterCoordinates]").val("");
		        $("form[name=ComplexFiltersForm]").find("input[name=filterDropCoordinates]").val("");
		        $("form[name=ComplexFiltersForm]").find("input[name=filterFrom]").val("0");        
		        $("form[name=ComplexFiltersForm]").find("input[name=filterTo]").val("20");
		
		        submitForm();
		      }     
		    });
		  }

			                           <div id="oneway">
												<b>At pick-up, some car hire companies will charge you a One Way Fee for dropping your car off at a different location. If you choose a car from one of these companies, we will tell you.</b></div>
				                     <script nonce="q9qsq10594e1qf6gbpc6lfj6ss">
											function findCheapestCar(carList) {
												var cheapestCar = carList.eq(0);
				                        		var cheapestPrice = parseFloat($('.carData > .price', cheapestCar).text());
				                        		//find leading price on non-recommended cars
				                        		carList.each(function() {
				                        			//Find first non-recommended car and compare with cheapest recommended. Will keep the cheapest one of them.
				                        			if($('.carData > .isRecommended', this).text() != '1') {
				                        				if(parseFloat($('.carData > .price', this).text()) <= cheapestPrice) {
				                        					cheapestCar = $(this);
				                        				}
				                        				return false; //Cheapest car decided, break iteration
				                        			}
				                        		});
				                        		
				                        		return cheapestCar;
											}
											
											function trackCarSelection(trigger, doGAQPush) {
				                        		var trackingStartMs = (new Date()).getTime();
				                        		var allCars = $('.car-result');
				                        		var triggerCar = $(trigger).closest('.car-result');
				                        		var category = $('.carData > .category', triggerCar).text();
				                        		var carsFromSameCategory = allCars.filter(function() {
				                        			return $('.carData > .category', this).text() == category; 
				                        		});
				                        		var recommendedCar = carsFromSameCategory.filter(function() {
				                        			return $('.carData > .isRecommended', this).text() == '1'; 
				                        		});
				                        		
				                        		var cheapestCar = findCheapestCar(allCars);
				                        		var cheapestInCategory = findCheapestCar(carsFromSameCategory);
				                        		
				                        		var positionWithinCategory = carsFromSameCategory.index(triggerCar);
				                        		var overallPosition = allCars.index(triggerCar);
				                        		
				                        		var value =  '#A,'+($(trigger).is('.button.green') ? 'B' : $(trigger).is('.result_mail') ? 'Q' : 'O')
				                        					+'#B,'+category
				                							+'#C,'+(recommendedCar.length > 0 ? $('.carData > .id', recommendedCar).text() : '')
				                        					+'#D,'+(recommendedCar.length > 0 ? $('.carData > .price', recommendedCar).text() : '')
				                        					+'#E,'+(recommendedCar.length > 0 ? parseFloat($('.rating_block .num', recommendedCar).text()) : '')
				                        					+'#F,'+(recommendedCar.length > 0 ? allCars.index(recommendedCar) : '')
				                        					+'#G,'+$('.carData > .id', cheapestCar).text()
				                        					+'#H,'+$('.carData > .price', cheapestCar).text()
				                        					+'#I,'+parseFloat($('.rating_block .num', cheapestCar).text())
				                        					+'#J,'+allCars.index(cheapestCar)
				                        					+'#K,'+$('.carData > .id', cheapestInCategory).text()
				                        					+'#L,'+$('.carData > .price', cheapestInCategory).text()
				                        					+'#M,'+parseFloat($('.rating_block .num', cheapestInCategory).text())
				                        					+'#N,'+allCars.index(cheapestInCategory)
				                        					+'#O,'+$('.carData > .id', triggerCar).text()
				                        					+'#P,'+$('.carData > .price', triggerCar).text()
				                        					+'#Q,'+parseFloat($('.rating_block .num', triggerCar).text())
				                        					+'#R,'+positionWithinCategory
				                        					+'#S,'+overallPosition
				                        					+'#T,'+carsFromSameCategory.length
				                        					+'#U,'+allCars.length
				                        					+'#V,'+((new Date()).getTime() - trackingStartMs)
				                        					+'#';

				                        		//DE logging
				                        		var trcrInput = $(document.BookingExtrasForm).find('name["trcr"]');
				                        		if(trcrInput.length == 0) {
				                        			trcrInput = $('<input/>').attr({
				                        				type: 'hidden',
				                        				name: 'trcr'
				                        			});
				                        			$(document.BookingExtrasForm).append(trcrInput);
				                        		}
				                        		
				                        		trcrInput.val(overallPosition+','+allCars.length+','+positionWithinCategory+','+carsFromSameCategory.length);
				                        		
				                        		var GAfn = doGAQPush ? GAQPush : GAQPushTransition;
				                        		GAfn('_trackEvent', 'ProductDetails', 'selectedCar', value, 1, true);
				                        	}
				                        </script>
									<script nonce="q9qsq10594e1qf6gbpc6lfj6ss">

                                                        GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'Fees one way', 'missing_info', missing_data_info, 1, true);
                                                    </script>

<script type="text/javascript" nonce="q9qsq10594e1qf6gbpc6lfj6ss">

    var group;
    if( $.cookies.get('group') != null ) {
        group = $.cookies.get('group');
    } else {
    	random = Math.floor(Math.random() * 3);
    	
    	if (random == 0)
    		group = 'A'
    	else if (random == 1)
    		group = 'B'
    	else
    		group = 'C';
    	if( typeof $.cookies != 'undefined' ) $.cookies.set('group', group, {expiresAt: new Date(2016, 01, 01, 12, 0, 0, 0), domain: '.rentalcars.com' });     
    }
    
    var category;
    if( $.cookies.get('category') != null ) {
    	category = $.cookies.get('category');
    } else {
        random = Math.floor(Math.random() * 3);
        
        if (random == 0)
        	category = 'A'
        else if (random == 1)
        	category = 'B'
        else
        	category = 'C';
        if( typeof $.cookies != 'undefined' ) $.cookies.set('category', category, {expiresAt: new Date(2016, 01, 01, 12, 0, 0, 0), domain: '.rentalcars.com' });     
    }
</script>

				function showAjaxRatings(clickedElem, supplierName, locNameEng, cityEn, countryEn, locName, vehicleId, locId, dropLocId) {
					GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'FE-5350', 'showRatings', supplierName, 1, true);
					clickedElem.css('cursor','progress');

					var data = {};

					data['layout'] = 'ratingsModal';
					data['supplierName'] = supplierName;
					data['locNameEng'] = locNameEng;
					data['cityEn'] = cityEn;
					data['countryEn'] = countryEn;
					data['locName'] = locName;
					data['vehicleId'] = vehicleId;
					data['locId'] = locId;
					data['dropLocId'] = dropLocId;
					
					
						data['location'] = locId;
						data['dropLocation'] = dropLocId;
						data['locationName'] = locName;
						data['dropLocationName'] = locName;
					
					$.ajax({
						url: "/RequestData.do",
						async: true,
						data: data,
						type: 'POST',
						success: function(data) {
							if($.trim(data) !== '') {
								var lightboxDiv = $('<div class="pop-up_outline supplierInfoPopup" style="display:none;"/>');
								lightboxDiv.append(data);
								lightboxDiv.lightbox_me({
									centered: true,
									overlayCSS: {background: '#fff', opacity: 0.8},
									destroyOnClose: true,
									lightboxSpeed: "slow"
								});
							}
							else{
								GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'FE-5350', 'emptyData', '', 1, true);
							}
						},
						error: function(jqXHR, textStatus, errorThrown){
							GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'FE-5350', 'ratingModalAjaxError', 'ajaxError', 1, true);
							if(jqXHR){
								var errorcode = 'ErrorCode:'+jqXHR.status;
								GAQPush('_trackEvent', 'FE-5350', 'ratingModalAjaxError', errorcode, 1, true);
							}
						},
						complete: function(jqXHR, textStatus, errorThrown){
							clickedElem.css('cursor','pointer');
						}
					});


				}
			</script>

<script nonce="q9qsq10594e1qf6gbpc6lfj6ss">
	/* UtmzUtils */
	(function() {

		var utmzCookieValues = null;

		function _getUtmzCookieValue() {
			var val = (document.cookie.match(/^(?:.*;)?\s__utmz=([^;]+)(?:.*)?$/)||[,null])[1];
			return val;
		}

		function _getUtmzCookieValues() {
			if (utmzCookieValues !== null) {
				return utmzCookieValues;
			}
			else {
				var utmzCookieValue = _getUtmzCookieValue();
				if (utmzCookieValue !== null) {
					var pairs = utmzCookieValue.split('.').slice(4).join('.').split('|');
					var ga = {};
					for (var i = 0; i < pairs.length; i++) {
						var temp = pairs[i].split('=');
						ga[temp[0]] = temp[1];
					}
					utmzCookieValues = ga;
					return utmzCookieValues;
				}
				else {
					utmzCookieValues = {};
					return utmzCookieValues;
				}
			}
		}

		function getValue(name) {
			var val = _getUtmzCookieValues()[name];
			return (typeof(val) !== 'undefined' ? val : '');
		}

		window.UtmzUtils = {
			getValue: getValue,
			_getUtmzCookieValue: _getUtmzCookieValue,
			_getUtmzCookieValues: _getUtmzCookieValues
		};

	})();
</script>

            		var ratio = 1;
            		// To account for zoom, change to use deviceXDPI instead of systemXDPI
            		if (window.screen.systemXDPI !== undefined && window.screen.logicalXDPI !== undefined && window.screen.systemXDPI > window.screen.logicalXDPI) {
            			// Only allow for values > 1
            			ratio = window.screen.systemXDPI / window.screen.logicalXDPI;

            		}

			  (function(){
				    function lpScriptLoader() {

				      var appendScript = function (src) {
				        if(document.createElement){
				          var script = document.createElement("script");
				          script.type = "text/javascript";
				          script.src = src;
				          document.body.appendChild(script);
				        }

				      };
				      appendScript("/js/live-engage.js");

				    }

				    if (window.attachEvent) {
				      window.attachEvent("onload", lpScriptLoader);
				    } else if (window.addEventListener) {
				      window.addEventListener("load", lpScriptLoader);
				    } else {
				      document.addEventListener("load", lpScriptLoader);
				    }

				  })();

				  (function(){

				    var firstTry = true,
				        tryAgain;

				    var _lpStopTrying = function () {
				      clearInterval(tryAgain);
				    };


				    // Set LivePerson running now the setup is complete
				    var startLETag = function() {
				      if (lpTag.start){
				      //Setting the isDom var to true because the dom already loaded
				        lpTag.isDom = true;

				        lpTag.start(); // call the start function
				        _lpStopTrying(); // cancel any repeat timers that are running


				      } else if (firstTry) {
				        firstTry = false;
				        tryAgain = setInterval(startLETag,100); // only set the timer on our firstTry = true
				      }


				    };
				    startLETag();


				  })();
		</script>

	    var exceptLastDot = url.substring(0, lastDot);
	    var secondToLastDot = exceptLastDot.lastIndexOf('.');
	    var topLevelDomain = url.substring(secondToLastDot, url.length);
